question: Within a radius of 180 kilometers, what restaurant can I find to the southeast of Nohra Haime Gallery, New York, NY?
sql:
WITH origin AS  (SELECT ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.005499 40.746428)',4326)::geography AS geometry)
SELECT * FROM pois, origin
WHERE ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.005499 40.746428)',4326)::geography, 180000)
AND amenity = 'restaurant'
AND degrees(ST_Azimuth(origin.geometry, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN 112.5 AND 157.5;
